   <h1>SIMPLIcity Architecture</h1>
   <br></br> 
<p><em><b>Image Semantics</b></em></p>
<p>Four levels
<ul>
   <li><b>Semantic Types</b></li>
   <p>Landscape Photograph, Textured/Graph Image</p><br>
   <li><b>Object Composition</b></li>
   <p>Sunset, Car Parked on a Beach</p><br>
   <li><b>Abstract Semantics</b></li>
   <p>People Fighting, Happy Person</p><br>
   <li><b>Detailed Semantics</b></li>
   <p>Detailed Description of a Given image</p><br>
</ul>
</p>
<p><em><b>Combine Semantic Classification and Image
Retrieval</b></em><br><br>
Narrow down the searching range in the database</p>
<p><em><b>Classification Examples for Picture Libraries</b></em>
<ul>
   <li>Graph vs Photograph</li>
   <li>Textured vs Non-textured</li>
   <li>Indoor vs Outdoor</li>
   <li>Objectionable vs Benign</li>
</ul>
</p>
